Description
Applicant
Represents an applicant for residential applications, including personal details and associated enquiries.

The ApplicantController handles the business logic for the applicant portal.

The ApplicantRepo class manages the persistence and retrieval of applicant data.

The ApplicantUI class provides the user interface (UI) for applicants in the portal.
